INDI Library Setup v0.2
=================

1) ./configure
2) make
3) su -c 'make install'
   Enter root password when prompted.
   
Refer to README for instructions on running indiserver and device drivers.



INDI CVS Setup
============

If you checkout INDI from the CVS, follow the instructions above. But before ./configure, type in:

make -f Makefile.cvs

That's it!
